Name: Anchor BanCorp Wisconsin Inc
Description: DELISTED - Anchor BanCorp Wisconsin Inc. operates as the holding company for AnchorBank, fsb that provides commercial banking services in Wisconsin. Its deposit products include passbook and statement savings accounts, non-interest bearing checking accounts, interest bearing checking accounts, money market deposit accounts, and certificates of deposit. The company?s loan products portfolio comprises residential loans; loans for commercial and business purposes, including letters of credit; commercial real estate loans, which include land and construction, multi-family, retail/office, and other commercial real estate loans; and consumer loans, such as express refinance first mortgage loans, second mortgage and home equity loans, vehicle loans, and other secured and unsecured loans for various consumer purposes. It has operation in approximately 50 locations. The company was founded in 1919 and is headquartered in Madison, Wisconsin.
